PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, NO. 5, TOMBSTONE TERRITORIAL PARK RESERVATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits, for an indefinite period, both prospecting and the staking of new mineral claims within an area identified as the Tombstone Territorial Park Reservation, and (b) revokes a similar Prohibition of Entry Order made by Order in Council P.C. 2000-144.
